{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">知道光的折射的概念；测定玻璃的折射率，掌握光发生折射时的特点。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><em>n</em>=sin<em>i</em>/sin<em>r</em></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">激光笔、玻璃砖</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.将激光笔从玻璃砖上表面斜射入玻璃砖；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.通过测量得到激光射入玻璃砖的入射角和折射角；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.通过</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>n</em>=sin<em>i</em>/sin<em>r</em></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">计算玻璃砖的折射率</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">实验所用玻璃砖的折射率为</span>1.5。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">光在不同介质中的速度不同，某种介质的折射率等于光在真空中的传播速度与光在这种介质中的传播速度之比，即<span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><em>n</em>=<em>c</em>/<em>v</em></span>。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}